          <li><strong>Days 11-17:</strong> Reply to every existing review. Set up a review-request habit: a text with a direct link to every customer at job completion.</li>
          <li><strong>Days 18-24:</strong> Build your highest-ticket service page first (usually soft-wash roof cleaning), fast on mobile, with a gallery and a one-tap quote button.</li>
          <li><strong>Days 25-30:</strong> Build your first neighborhood page for your strongest service area. Add a maintenance-plan offer to your closing process so one-time jobs convert to annual accounts.</li>
        </ol>

